  "prompt": "What are the best Indian gaming companies that builds small open world, first-person shooter, 3d games for Ios that you can hire so they can make games for you?",
  "response": "If you're looking to hire Indian gaming companies that specialize in developing open-world, first-person shooter, 3D games for iOS, consider these established companies:\n\n1. **Octro Inc.** - Known for mobile game development, Octro has experience in multiple genres and could potentially handle complex game types like open-world, first-person shooters.\n\n2. **Dhruva Interactive** - With a rich history in game development, Dhruva Interactive has worked on various popular games and offers services for creating detailed and interactive 3D environments.\n\n3. **Nazara Technologies** - Nazara is prominent in mobile gaming with expertise across various game genres. They could leverage their resources and experience to develop high-quality FPS games for iOS.\n\n4. **HashCube** - Primarily in mobile game development, HashCube's team can manage innovative game design and engaging user experience, which is crucial for open-world FPS games.\n\n5. **nCORE Games** - nCORE specializes in action-packed games and has developed very popular titles. Their experience in developing engaging and high-performance mobile games makes them a strong candidate.\n\n6. **Hypernova Interactive** - Known for their creative approach and visually appealing games, Hypernova can deliver immersive open-world, first-person shooters.\n\n7. **Games2win** - With extensive experience in developing mobile games, Games2win has the technical prowess to create engaging 3D games.\n\nWhen approaching these companies, it's important to review their portfolios, discuss your specific requirements, and understand their development processes to ensure they can meet your needs.",
